rComments: Horrible. Didn't get a single assignment or test back until the last discussion of the semester! She screwed over the entire class with grades. The highest grade on our midterm was a 91, no curve. Avoid this TA at all costs. The material was great, the class is very interesting, however not worth the frustration of dealing with this TA
She handled a lot of angry students and gave everybody a chance to review their grades. Pretty amazing TA if you ask me.
She was the TA when I took the class, and she was in charge of grades.  She screwed over half of the class on the final.  Avoid any class where she's the TA.
